verses.text:
One more day's work for Je-sus, One less of life for me;
But heav'n is near-er, And Christ is dear-er,
Than yes-ter-day to me; His love and light Fill all my sight, His will is peace for me.

One more day's work for Je-sus, One more day to praise his name;
And rest comes sweet-er, And rest comes sweet-er,
And rest comes sweet-er, And rest comes sweet-er.

One more day's work for Je-sus, O yes, A wea-ry day, but how glor-ious;
And rest comes sweet-er, For work is done; And rest comes sweet-er,
And rest comes sweet-er, For work is done.
